OL,5,G1550 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe second visit is to Glencoe
OL,7,     FVilla Guest House in Featherstone,
OL,8,     FWest Yorkshire, owned by Ewa Hunt.
OL,9,     FBut the homely bedrooms aren't to
OL,10,     Feveryone's taste and there's a
OL,11,     Fdebate over dinner.
OL,12,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FUncle and nephew Stefan Carron and
OL,14,     FNick Edwards host at The Fox Inn
OL,15,     Fin Stourton, Staffordshire. Will
OL,16,     FStefan's celebrity name dropping
OL,17,     Fimpress their guests?
