OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FTony Carlin and his partner
OL,7,     FNatalie Briggs host the final
OL,8,     Fvisit, at The New Inn in
OL,9,     FDerbyshire. But some of the guests
OL,10,     Fquestion its 'luxury' label, and
OL,11,     Fthere's a no-show at breakfast.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,14,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet to
OL,15,     Ffind out how much they've been
OL,16,     Fpaid. After dramatic discoveries
OL,17,     Fand cutting comments, the winner
OL,18,     Fis announced.
