OL,5,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,6,     FGeorge Clarke helps Joanna and
OL,7,     FSimon to transform their monster
OL,8,     FVictorian semi in Margate, and
OL,9,     Fvisits a beautiful Grade II listed
OL,10,     FGeorgian manor conversion in
OL,11,     FWorthing.
OL,12,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,13,     FIn Southampton, Kirstie helps
OL,14,     FAntoinette and Matt revive their
OL,15,     Fattempts to get on the property
OL,16,     Fladder. And Phil's with Catherine
OL,17,     Fwho wants a fresh start in
OL,18,     Fcharming Chichester.
