OL,5,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,6,     FWhen he lost three limbs in
OL,7,     FAfghanistan, Jon's life changed
OL,8,     Fforever. Now he wants to build a
OL,9,     Fhouse that allows him to live
OL,10,     Findependently. The design's
OL,11,     Fcutting edge, but the budget
OL,12,     Fspirals.
OL,13,G2100 Bill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,14,     FIn Hanoi, Bill explores Vietnam's
OL,15,     Fcomplex relationship with life,
OL,16,     Fdeath and war, and a culture
OL,17,     Fdefined by spirituality and
OL,18,     Ffemininity, and remembers the
OL,19,     Fpeople who he's lost. (Ep4)
