OL,6,     F...to the Orchestra: Let Bill be
OL,7,     Fyour guide as he joins forces with
OL,8,     Fmaestro Anne Dudley and the BBC
OL,9,     FConcert Orchestra for a humorous
OL,10,     Ffusion of music and comedy at the
OL,11,     FRoyal Albert Hall.
OL,12,G2315 24 Hours in A&E
OL,13,     FGraham, who's 50, is rushed to
OL,14,     FKing's after having a suspected
OL,15,     Fheart attack. Pat, who's 71, is
OL,16,     Fbrought in after her husband Bill
OL,17,     Ffound her unconscious at home.
